@database SG&S-Cut1.GUIDE
@node MAIN "SG&S-Cut v1.0"

	Before reading this you shuld read ScreenGrab&Save3.0.GUIDE !

	@{"     SRPSKI     " link S-1}
	@{"     ENGLISH    " link E-1}







@endnode
@node S-1 "Srpski"

	Primetno je da neke ne AGA igre i ekrani uopste prilikom koriscenja
SG&S-a dobijaju duplikate sa desne strane i to sa izmenjenim bojama (?) .
Zato sam napisao ovaj mali program koji ce otseci nezeljeni deo slike.
Takodje ovim programom mozete konvertovati BitMape u IFF slike.

	Upotreba:
OPCIJA: Screen - prvo trebate odrediti velicinu ekrana.Uzmite one dimenzije
	         koje odgovaraju pravoj slici.
		 Na raspolaganju su 320x256 , 640x256 i 640x512.
OPCIJA: File - Odredite nacin kako ce slika biti snimljena tj file
		Overvrite - snima isecenu sliku preko stare
		Append 2IFF - uzima ime starog fajla i dodaje imenu novog 
			      fajla 2IFF
		Append _SG&S-Cut1 - uzima ime starog fajla i dodaje imenu 
                                    novog fajla _SG&S-Cut1

OPCIJA: LoadPalette? - Dali zelite da ucitate i paletu fajla.Ovo je jako
		       vazno.IFF-ILBM slike imaju paletu a BitMape je nemaju!

GADZET: CUT IT NOW - pokrece postupak secenja sa prethodno izabranim opcijama.

GADZET: NO MORE CUTS... - izlaz iz programa

	Ovaj program je malo bagovit i treba mu dorada.Priznajem.Zato ce
biti doradjen u verziji 2.0 . I ovde primam predloge itd. bilo koje vrste.

@endnode
@node E-1 "ENGLISH"

	I noticed that some NON-AGA games and screens in general,under
usage of SG&S,gain duplicates on their right side with axchanged colors (?).
So i wrote this small program for cuting unwanted part of image.Also this
program could be used for converting BitMaps into IFF images.

	USAGE:

OPTION: Screen - first determine size of screen.Take original image size.
		 Avalaible screens are 320x256 , 640x256 and 640x512.

OPTION: File - determine filename.If option is set to Overvrite then loaded
             image will be overvriten with cuted image.
             If option is seted to Append 2IFF/_SG&S-Cut1 then new
             file will be saved vith old name + this append on original name.

OPTION: Load Palette? - Will palette be loaded from file or not.Be careful 
			with this.IFF images have palette ,but BitMaps not.


GADGET: CUT IT NOW! - start cuting and saving images.

GADGET: NO MORE CUTS... - Quit program.

	This program has some bugs.I admit.But it will be corrected in v2.0!
@endnode
